n>\n    <link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/fonts/main.woff2\" as=\"font\" type=\"font/woff2\" crossorigin>\n    \n    <meta name=\"theme-color\" content=\"#4CAF50\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <h1>Welcome to WebLearn Academy</h1>\n</body>\n</html>"
